    <item>
      <title>Starmer 将于本周启动 GB Energy 投资者特别工作组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/starmer-to-launch-gb-energy-investors-task-force-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新任首相基尔·斯塔默本周将启动英国能源公司（Great British Energy），这是一家旨在刺激清洁能源投资的上市公司，同时还将召集一个商业工作组为设立国家财富基金提供建议，他的政府希望借此表明自己已迈出了第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/starmer-to-launch-gb-energy-investors-task-force-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:33:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一家能源公司即将为 2800 万巴西人提供水资源管理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/equatorial-eqtl3-to-manage-water-for-millions-in-sabesp-sbsp3-privatization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西人口最多的州即将把拉丁美洲最大水务公司的战略股权出售给一家价值 70 亿美元的能源分销商，后者两年前才开始涉足卫生领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/equatorial-eqtl3-to-manage-water-for-millions-in-sabesp-sbsp3-privatization</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼称关键矿产资源争夺战愈演愈烈 美国必须投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/indonesia-says-us-must-invest-as-critical-minerals-race-picks-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼外交部副部长帕哈拉·曼苏里表示，美国等发达国家需要向拥有大量关键矿产资源的国家进行投资，以降低供应链风险，因为这些大宗商品是推动地缘政治的“新石油”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/indonesia-says-us-must-invest-as-critical-minerals-race-picks-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道格·伯古姆 (Doug Burgum) 赢得特朗普和捐助者的青睐，成为副总统候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/trump-vp-contender-doug-burgum-charms-donors-ceos-to-gain-prominence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年这个时候，选民们还不知道道格·伯古姆这个名字。为了与其他共和党总统初选候选人一起辩论，他不得不送出 20 美元的礼品卡，以换取 1 美元的竞选捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/trump-vp-contender-doug-burgum-charms-donors-ceos-to-gain-prominence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预算缺口扩大，匈牙利提高银行暴利税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/hungary-raises-windfall-taxes-on-banks-to-plug-budget-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利宣布对银行征收新税，并取消了削减针对目标行业的暴利税的计划，因为新数据显示预算赤字进一步扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/hungary-raises-windfall-taxes-on-banks-to-plug-budget-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称全国袭击已造成十余人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/kyiv-comes-under-attack-in-missile-strike-across-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰称，该国空军报告称，俄罗斯向乌克兰全国发射了多枚弹道导弹，对基辅一家儿童医院造成损坏，造成数十人死亡和受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/kyiv-comes-under-attack-in-missile-strike-across-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:54:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大选后谨慎买家涌现，法国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国股市上涨，扭转了早盘的跌势，因为在左翼政党意外获胜、议会出现分裂且没有明显多数的情况下，投资者将选举结果视为“最不坏”的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国撤回吊销罢工医生执照的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-08/urgent-south-korea-to-withdraw-plan-to-suspend-licenses-of-striking-doctors-to-resolve-medical-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社）——韩国政府周一宣布，将放弃吊销罢工初级医生执照的计划，这是说服他们重返工作岗位并解决该国长达数月的医疗僵局的努力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-08/urgent-south-korea-to-withdraw-plan-to-suspend-licenses-of-striking-doctors-to-resolve-medical-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 05:28:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风贝丽尔横扫墨西哥后登陆德克萨斯州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/beryl-regaining-strength-on-track-to-reach-texas-as-hurricane</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风贝丽尔于周一凌晨登陆德克萨斯州海岸，横扫加勒比海和墨西哥湾后带来暴雨和危及生命的风暴潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/beryl-regaining-strength-on-track-to-reach-texas-as-hurricane</guid>
